nl_querry: Please give more information about the Formula_1 races that used the Silverstone Circuit. more information refers to url
llm_querry: SELECT `R`.`name` AS `RaceName`, `R`.`url` AS `RaceURL` FROM `races` AS `R` JOIN `circuits` AS `C` ON `R`.`circuitId` = `C`.`circuitId` WHERE `C`.`name` = 'Silverstone Circuit' ORDER BY `R`.`year`;
gold_querry: SELECT DISTINCT T1.url FROM circuits AS T1 INNER JOIN races AS T2 ON T2.circuitID = T1.circuitId WHERE T1.name = 'Silverstone Circuit'
